flowchart LR
    U[Student User] --> UI[HallPass Web Interface]
    UI --> SEARCH[Search / Filter Campus Information]
    UI --> REVIEW[Review / Rating Submission Form]
    UI --> GUIDE[Campus Survival Guide Page]

    SEARCH --> STORE[(HallPass Data Storage)]
    REVIEW --> STORE
    GUIDE --> STORE

    STORE --> LIST[Review and Guide List]
    LIST --> DETAIL[Campus Place / Guide Detail View]
    STORE --> DASH[Review Summary / Admin Dashboard]

    ADMIN[Campus Administrator] --> ADMINP[Admin Panel]
    ADMINP --> STORE
    ADMINP --> MOD[Review Moderation / Content Update]
    MOD --> STORE
